      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Control UI service-worker activation broadcast and browser reload listener so open tabs reload when a new service worker version activates.\n\nPR surface: Source +19. Total +19 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: stale Control UI protocol ranges are rejected by the gateway, current main and v2026.6.9 lack an activation reload path, and the linked issue supplies a cloud/token stale-service-worker scenario. I did not run a live Zeabur or Chrome stale-service-worker upgrade reproduction in this read-only review.",
